&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Metrics &amp;amp; Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Define and track KPIs related to quoting efficiency, operational accuracy, launch velocity, adoption, and process health.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
