&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;7+ years of experience in Technical Product Management, with significant exposure to Quote-to-Order systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
