&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Hands-on experience with Salesforce CPQ, including product modeling, pricing logic, discounting, bundling, approvals, and templating&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with IronClad CLM for contract lifecycle management and NetSuite ERP for downstream financials.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Proven track record leading cross-functional QTO initiatives in SaaS or high-growth enterprise environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Strong technical foundation — familiarity with APIs, data flows, and system integrations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Exceptional ability to translate business requirements into technical solutions and product roadmaps.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent organizational and communication skills to manage multiple priorities and stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Skills​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Salesforce certifications (CPQ Specialist, Administrator, Architect).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with IronClad and Netsuite.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Experience working in public company environments with strong governance and process controls.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Background in automating and scaling workflows across multiple interconnected systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Background in software engineering (to better serve our Product integrations).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;#LI-HYBRID&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;#LI-AM1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The compensation range displayed on this job posting reflects the minimum and maximum target for new hire compensation for the target position and level, and may include sales incentives or target bonuses depending on the role. &amp;nbsp;Our compensation ranges are determined by role, level, and location. Our job titles may span more than one career level. Within the range, individual compensation is determined by additional factors, including job-related skills, experience, relevant education or training, business need, market demands. The compensation range is subject to change and may be modified in the future. Your recruiter can share more about the specific compensation range for your location during the hiring process.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Oakland Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$180,884&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$226,105.50 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.3;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Perks and Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;100% employer-paid medical insurance&lt;strong&gt;*&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous paid time-off policy (PTO), plus paid sick time, inclusive parental leave policy, holidays, and volunteer days off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RSU stock grants*&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional development and training opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company virtual happy hours, free food, and fun team-building activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly cell phone stipend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to an innovative mental health support platform that offers personalized care and resources in areas such as: therapy, coaching, and self-guided mindfulness exercises for all covered employees and their covered dependents.&lt;/li&gt;
